                            <comment id="17800409" author="simplejason" created="Tue, 26 Dec 2023 06:06:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Feedback is welcome, I can submit a PR to remove the husky dependency on the front end : )&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17800411" author="JIRAUSER281639" created="Tue, 26 Dec 2023 06:15:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for raising this issue! &#128516; I completely agree with your proposal to make front-end code detection an optional command execution in our use of husky with runtime-web. By doing this, we can preserve the functionality of any globally configured git hooks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
